// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Seven-stage spine (FORA-50 spec §2.3 + architecture.md §3)
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
⋮----
/**
 * The seven SDLC stages, in strict order. The Orchestrator refuses to skip a
 * stage (see `STAGE_SPINE`). `done` is a run-state terminal, not a stage.
 */
