 *   Reverse path  (router → engine)
 *     approval_decided{accept}          ──► engine.advance(...)
 *     approval_decided{request_changes} ──► engine.reEnter(...) (stage_returned)
 *     approval_decided{reject}          ──► engine.pauseRun(...)
 *     approval_expired                  ──► engine.pauseRun(...)
