# Each entry names one cloud Acme has granted Forge access to. The
# broker's trust probe verifies the role ARN parses, the expected
# issuer/audience match what the broker mints, and (in phase 2) the
# customer's trust policy actually accepts a canary assume. A tenant
# with a probe failure is in `cloud_disabled` state until the entry
